tabs.title: Create GoldFlights
tabs.text:
.create async materialized-view  with (backfill=true,dimensionTables = dynamic(["SilverAircrafts", "SilverCallsigns"])) GoldFlights on table SilverOpenskynet
{ 
    SilverOpenskynet
    | project-rename openskynet_bronze_timestamp=bronze_timestamp, openskynet_silver_timestamp=silver_timestamp
    | join kind=leftouter valid_aircrafts on icao24
    | join kind=inner valid_callsigns on callsign
    | extend flights_gold_timestamp = now()
    | extend current_position_wkt = strcat('POINT(', longitude, " ", latitude, ')')
    | extend origin_position_wkt = strcat('POINT(', origin_longitude, " ", origin_latitude, ')')
    | extend destination_position_wkt = strcat('POINT(', destination_longitude, " ", destination_latitude, ')')
    | extend linestring_wkt = strcat("LINESTRING(", geojson_linestring.coordinates,")")
    | extend linestring_wkt = replace_string(linestring_wkt, ",", " ")
    | extend linestring_wkt = replace_string(linestring_wkt, "[", "")
    | extend linestring_wkt = replace_string(linestring_wkt, "] ", ", ")
    | extend linestring_wkt = replace_string(linestring_wkt, "]", "")
    | project-away callsign1, icao241
    | summarize arg_max(openskynet_bronze_timestamp, *) by icao24, callsign
}
